{"tid":1284633,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"教協：董建華言論侮辱通識科教師","createTime":"2019-07-04T08:55:46.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-04T08:56:57.000Z","uid":212626,"like":19,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"94d6d52b79bc6c394d94e29efe90db55547c8dcc","tid":1284633,"uid":212626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-04T08:55:46.000Z","msg":"全國政協副主席、前行政長官董建華昨日表示，其任內推行的通識教育是造成現時年輕人問題的主因之一。教協理事、通識科老師方景樂批評有關指控，是對前線教師是極大侮辱。<br />\n<br />\n方景樂表示，按教育專業守則，通識科老師以客觀理性態度與學生討論時政，並非作政治信念的灌輸，他願意邀請相關人士上一節通識課。<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://www2.hkej.com/instantnews/current/article/2183080/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww2.hkej.com%2Finstantnews%2Fcurrent%2Farticle%2F2183080%2F&d=3FM1mHFWgl829bPTLnnFI7eFZk%2BLn%2Bp4m9s6a9hK%2BPA%3D&h=65494d70\" target=\"_blank\">https://www2.hkej.com/instantnews/current/article/2183080/</a>"},{"pid":"137abce7564889af6c9d630a91c0150c6730d0e1","tid":1284633,"uid":123848,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-04T08:56:57.000Z","msg":"喺時候狗咬狗骨<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/fight_connect.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}